; =============================================================================
; PalWorldSettings.ini.example
; Copy to PalWorldSettings.ini and edit before hosting publicly.
; NEVER commit PalWorldSettings.ini with real passwords.
;
; Crossplay (Steam + Xbox / PC Game Pass):
;   CrossplayPlatforms=(Steam,Xbox)
;   bUseAuth=True
;   Launch with -publiclobby (already in scripts/start_server.ps1)
;
; PvP: OFF by default. To enable PvP set ALL THREE to True:
;   bIsPvP, bEnablePlayerToPlayerDamage, bEnableDefenseOtherGuildPlayer
; =============================================================================

